{{about|all programs that were broadcast on Disney Channel|a list that only includes programs that were originally broadcast on and produced at least partially by Disney Channel|List of Disney Channel series}} {{pp-vandalism|small=yes}} {{Use mdy dates|date=July 2017}} This is a list of television programs currently broadcast (in first-run or reruns), scheduled to be broadcast or formerly broadcast on [[Disney Channel]], a family-oriented American basic cable channel and former [[premium channel]], owned by [[The Walt Disney Company]]. The channel was launched on April 18, 1983, and airs a mix of animated and live-action programming, ranging from action to drama to comedy.
