* 2005
** July: [[Hurricane Dennis]] occurs.
** [[Historic Centre of Cienfuegos]] designated an UNESCO [[World Heritage Site]].
* 2014 - Population: 149,129.<ref>{{cite web |url= http://unstats.un.org/unsd/demographic/products/dyb/dyb2014.htm |work=Demographic Yearbook 2014 |publisher=[[United Nations Statistics Division]] |title=Population of Capital Cities and Cities of 100,000 or More Inhabitants }}</ref>

